Eva Thatcher https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eva_Thatcher 0 Eva Thatcher (March 14, 1862 – September 28, 1942) was an American film actress. She appeared in more than one hundred films between 1912 and 1930. She was born in Omaha, Nebraska, and died in Los Angeles, California.
